WEBVTT

00:00.489 --> 00:02.188
Previously on <i>Fringe...</i>

00:02.195 --> 00:04.061
What's wrong?
I've just been getting these migraines.

00:04.257 --> 00:05.923
That's all. Tomorrow I'm gonna send
some medication over.

00:05.954 --> 00:07.421
It's a new drug
we've been working on.

00:07.471 --> 00:10.057
- You don't have to do that.
- I want to.

00:10.125 --> 00:12.292
I'm the closest thing
you have to a mother, remember?

00:12.344 --> 00:13.677
In the dreams
that you were having,

00:13.762 --> 00:15.963
the ones that I'm in,
did you feel like you knew me?

00:16.014 --> 00:19.016
You were a stranger.
What would I feel?

00:19.101 --> 00:21.185
I love you.

00:21.269 --> 00:22.987
Look, Peter, I don't know
how to explain it.

00:23.071 --> 00:25.472
Feels like there was
somebody else in my head.

00:25.524 --> 00:27.408
Hi. Come in.

00:27.475 --> 00:29.326
Gonna pour you a drink.

00:29.411 --> 00:30.811
What is that that
smells so fantastic?

00:30.862 --> 00:32.530
What do you mean?
It's Friday.

00:32.613 --> 00:35.315
I ordered Damiano's.

00:35.367 --> 00:38.452
Whoa. Olivia.

00:42.541 --> 00:44.158
<i>Just be straight with me.</i>

00:44.209 --> 00:45.176
<i>Are you okay?</i>

00:45.260 --> 00:48.328
Yeah, I'm fine.

00:48.380 --> 00:49.647
Then why did you kiss me?

00:53.885 --> 00:55.052
I don't know.

00:55.137 --> 00:56.637
It just felt like
that's what we'd do.

00:56.688 --> 00:59.473
Just felt normal.

01:03.695 --> 01:05.429
How long have we known
each other, Olivia?

01:08.867 --> 01:11.068
Three months.

01:11.153 --> 01:13.037
Peter, I know who you are,
and I know who I am.

01:13.121 --> 01:14.705
I think that this
may just be

01:14.790 --> 01:17.825
some residual effects left over
from being in Westfield.

01:17.876 --> 01:19.710
Then we should let Walter
have a look at you.

01:19.795 --> 01:22.046
No, I'm--I'm fine.
Honestly.

01:22.130 --> 01:26.217
I think what I need
is just some rest.

01:26.301 --> 01:27.551
I'm sorry that I kissed you.

01:27.636 --> 01:31.538
To be honest, I'm a little bit
embarrassed about it.

01:31.590 --> 01:33.390
There's no need
to be embarrassed.

01:36.845 --> 01:38.479
Maybe I should stay here
for a little while--

01:38.546 --> 01:39.814
you know, just while you rest,
in case.

01:39.881 --> 01:42.483
I would really like
some time to myself.

01:42.550 --> 01:46.437
I think I've got another
migraine coming on.

01:50.892 --> 01:52.193
Okay.

01:52.244 --> 01:53.444
If you're still feeling
this way in the morning,

01:53.528 --> 01:55.079
will you please let Walter
take a look at you?

01:55.163 --> 01:57.581
Okay.

02:01.920 --> 02:03.537
Hi.
Come on in.

02:10.428 --> 02:13.280
<i>Shh, quiet, quiet.</i>

02:13.348 --> 02:16.467
We're almost there.

02:18.000 --> 02:24.074
