02:27.946 --> 02:29.530
It's time.

02:58.760 --> 02:59.843
He's in the kitchen.

03:03.315 --> 03:05.349
Oh, hot, hot.

03:05.433 --> 03:06.417
Fan out.

03:06.484 --> 03:08.018
You two, fan out.

03:11.072 --> 03:12.973
Be careful.

03:16.945 --> 03:18.445
Sean.

03:18.496 --> 03:19.914
Hey, what are you doing
in here?

03:19.981 --> 03:21.198
You should be in bed.

03:21.283 --> 03:23.334
<i>Sean, it's me,</i>
<i>Bernadette.</i>

03:23.418 --> 03:24.618
Okay? Come on.

03:24.669 --> 03:25.869
I'm gonna take you back
to your room.

03:25.954 --> 03:27.121
He's in the kitchen.

03:27.172 --> 03:29.089
<i>Let's go.</i>
<i>Come on.</i>

03:35.180 --> 03:36.880
He's coming your way.

03:36.965 --> 03:37.831
He's coming your way.

03:37.882 --> 03:40.017
Sean, can you hear me?
Sean.

03:40.101 --> 03:42.136
Listen, the voices
that you're hearing,

03:42.187 --> 03:44.338
they're not real.

03:44.389 --> 03:47.474
You're okay.
Let's go.

03:51.012 --> 03:57.017
♪

03:59.371 --> 04:01.705
Please.

04:01.790 --> 04:03.357
<i>Please, take anything</i>
<i>you want.</i>

04:03.408 --> 04:04.875
You don't have to do this.

04:04.960 --> 04:06.961
<i>No, no, please, please!</i>

04:07.028 --> 04:08.295
I beg you.
No, no, no!

04:08.363 --> 04:11.548
No!

04:11.633 --> 04:12.716
<i>Damn it, I'm cut!</i>

04:12.801 --> 04:13.717
<i>I'm bleeding!</i>

04:15.720 --> 04:18.255
Charles!
There's three of us and one of him.

04:18.339 --> 04:20.224
I need some help, Charles!
Hold him down, damn it!

04:23.094 --> 04:24.311
This one's severe.

04:24.379 --> 04:27.398
That's better.

04:27.482 --> 04:28.983
I'm gonna sedate him.

04:46.201 --> 04:47.251
<i>It's over.</i>

04:47.335 --> 04:49.920
He's dead. It's over.

04:55.397 --> 04:59.397
